ght the whole exchange between himself and isenberg on tape golden coffin controversyedit also at the nabors annual shareholders june   meeting a stockholder proposal calling for investor approval of executive death benefits at nabors industries was voted down amalgamated banks longview funds owns  shares in nabors sponsored the proposal amalgamated proposed that nabors get shareholder approval for agreements that award unearned salary bonuses and other compensation to executives estates if they die these arrangements are called golden coffins nabors had urged its shareholders to vote against the proposal in april nabors renegotiated new death benefit packages for ceo eugene isenberg and coo anthony petrello lowering the total collective payments by more than  million jet abuse investigationedit a june   wall street journal story reviewing faa records reported that nabors had failed to provide a dollar figure for the cost of aircraft use by ceo eugene isenberg during  and  according to the article nabors jet fleet often flew to resort destinations including palm beach and marthas vineyard per wsj estimates those flights alone would have cost over  an amount that far exceeds the sec rules which require disclosure of the cost of any personal travel that exceeds corporate jet set leisure vs business corporate affairsedit the houston office is located in greenspoint in march  nabors said it plans to cut  jobs in response to falling upstream activity amid slumping oil prices the company will cut  percent of its sales staff and  percent of its us drilling workforce see alsoedit houston portal companies portal energy portal list of oilfield service companies referencesedit  a b nabors industries ltd nbrnyse company description business week  a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o standard  poors stock guide various issues  a b c d e nabors industries ltd sec schedule a notice of  annual general meeting of shareholders may    a b anglo energy limited  ucla bankruptcy research databa